694/******************** Bit definition for ADC_ISR register *******************/
695#define ADC_ISR_ADRDY_Pos (0U)
696#define ADC_ISR_ADRDY_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_ADRDY_Pos)
697#define ADC_ISR_ADRDY ADC_ISR_ADRDY_Msk
698#define ADC_ISR_EOSMP_Pos (1U)
699#define ADC_ISR_EOSMP_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_EOSMP_Pos)
700#define ADC_ISR_EOSMP ADC_ISR_EOSMP_Msk
701#define ADC_ISR_EOC_Pos (2U)
702#define ADC_ISR_EOC_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_EOC_Pos)
703#define ADC_ISR_EOC ADC_ISR_EOC_Msk
704#define ADC_ISR_EOS_Pos (3U)
705#define ADC_ISR_EOS_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_EOS_Pos)
706#define ADC_ISR_EOS ADC_ISR_EOS_Msk
707#define ADC_ISR_OVR_Pos (4U)
708#define ADC_ISR_OVR_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_OVR_Pos)
709#define ADC_ISR_OVR ADC_ISR_OVR_Msk
710#define ADC_ISR_AWD1_Pos (7U)
711#define ADC_ISR_AWD1_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_AWD1_Pos)
712#define ADC_ISR_AWD1 ADC_ISR_AWD1_Msk
713#define ADC_ISR_AWD2_Pos (8U)
714#define ADC_ISR_AWD2_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_AWD2_Pos)
715#define ADC_ISR_AWD2 ADC_ISR_AWD2_Msk
716#define ADC_ISR_AWD3_Pos (9U)
717#define ADC_ISR_AWD3_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_AWD3_Pos)
718#define ADC_ISR_AWD3 ADC_ISR_AWD3_Msk
719#define ADC_ISR_EOCAL_Pos (11U)
720#define ADC_ISR_EOCAL_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_EOCAL_Pos)
721#define ADC_ISR_EOCAL ADC_ISR_EOCAL_Msk
722#define ADC_ISR_CCRDY_Pos (13U)
723#define ADC_ISR_CCRDY_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_ISR_CCRDY_Pos)
724#define ADC_ISR_CCRDY ADC_ISR_CCRDY_Msk
726/* Legacy defines */
727#define ADC_ISR_EOSEQ (ADC_ISR_EOS)
728
729/******************** Bit definition for ADC_IER register *******************/
730#define ADC_IER_ADRDYIE_Pos (0U)
731#define ADC_IER_ADRDYIE_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_IER_ADRDYIE_Pos)
732#define ADC_IER_ADRDYIE ADC_IER_ADRDYIE_Msk
733#define ADC_IER_EOSMPIE_Pos (1U)
734#define ADC_IER_EOSMPIE_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_IER_EOSMPIE_Pos)
735#define ADC_IER_EOSMPIE ADC_IER_EOSMPIE_Msk
736#define ADC_IER_EOCIE_Pos (2U)
737#define ADC_IER_EOCIE_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_IER_EOCIE_Pos)
738#define ADC_IER_EOCIE ADC_IER_EOCIE_Msk
739#define ADC_IER_EOSIE_Pos (3U)
740#define ADC_IER_EOSIE_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_IER_EOSIE_Pos)
741#define ADC_IER_EOSIE ADC_IER_EOSIE_Msk
742#define ADC_IER_OVRIE_Pos (4U)
743#define ADC_IER_OVRIE_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_IER_OVRIE_Pos)
744#define ADC_IER_OVRIE ADC_IER_OVRIE_Msk
745#define ADC_IER_AWD1IE_Pos (7U)
746#define ADC_IER_AWD1IE_Msk (0x1UL << ADC_IER_AWD1IE_Pos)
747#define ADC_IER_AWD1IE ADC_IER_AWD1IE_Msk
